Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:16.81,Font,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\i1}Just having you in my line of sight is enough to draw breath{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:25.79,Font,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\i1}For someone like me,\Nthat alone should be my redemption, and yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:32.26,Font,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\i1}Tiny me repeats nothing but mistakes over and over again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:39.43,Font,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\i1}How much strength must I gain to live without leaving wounds behind?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:46.13,Font,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\i1}I will live on, believing in this love, without wavering{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:52.38,Font,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\i1}Clutching these wounds that never close,\NI will keep them healing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:58.42,Font,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\i1}We'll march together,\Nwe will keep walking{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:01:04.53,Font,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\i1}Because behind us,\Nthere is no returning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:10.60,Font,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\i1}Even now,\Nit's still causing me pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:16.44,Font,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\i1}Deep in my chest,\Nthe unerasable sin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:19.49,Font,,0,0,0,,{\fs50}Darling.